  <summary date="2022-06-24T21:17:10Z" status="Introduced in House">Ending Payments to Non-American Citizens Act

This bill prohibits making amounts from the Judgment Fund available to an alien who is not a lawful permanent resident unless specifically authorized by law. (The Judgment Fund is an account for paying judgments and settlements against the United States.)</summary>
